<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q7_v11" title="Q7_v11" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un recorrido de 36 km, se representa en una barra la ruta completa dividida en tres tramos consecutivos, uno por cada día.</p>
    <p>En la barra, el primer tramo, marcado como "Día 1", corresponde a 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      de la ruta total. Del tramo restante, se indica que 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      está sombreado como "Día 2" y el tramo final corresponde al "Día 3". ¿Cuántos kilómetros se recorrieron el segundo día?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">24<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El Día 1 es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, por lo que quedan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El Día 2 corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, no a 24 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">18<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El Día 1 es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. Entonces quedan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El segundo día se recorre <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">6<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Después del Día 1 quedan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El Día 2 es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. Además, 6 km es solo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y no coincide con el tramo pedido.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">27<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Los 27 km corresponden al tramo restante después del Día 1, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero el Día 2 es solo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, no 27 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular lo recorrido el Día 1</strong></p>
            <p>El primer día corresponde a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del total de 36 km.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, el Día 1 se recorren 9 km.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular el tramo restante después del Día 1</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Después del primer día quedan 27 km por recorrer.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular lo recorrido el Día 2</strong></p>
            <p>El segundo día corresponde a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del tramo restante.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, el segundo día se recorren 18 km.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Verificación</strong></p>
            <p>Si el Día 2 fue 18 km, para el Día 3 quedan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Así, los tres días suman:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>La suma coincide con la ruta total.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La respuesta correcta es 18 km, alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>